{
  "stem": "5471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when she came in the camp, she was put in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the hospital was marvelous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they looked very well after her, and they got her to walk again and be healthy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when she was better and she was healthy, she was sent on transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, that gave the people inside the camp the idea, see, they try to get to us all healthy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we are healthy, they send us out to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, when the woman came there, one or two days later, she was gassed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But no one was-- knew about it in that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We tried everything possible to-- to know what really happened in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "For instance, my husband had a girl working for him, Leah Hertha-- Hertha Leah Alexander.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she often came to my place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when she went on transport with her brother, I said, Hertha do me a pleasure.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Write a little card when you are in the camp, and when you really can't talk about it, instead of Hertha Leah write Leah Hertha.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then I know I have to read exactly the opposite from what you are writing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She said good idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I promise I'll do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We never got a card.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were never allowed to send a card.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She survived, but she never had a chance to send anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we tried-- people to put paper in the-- in the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had places in the train try to hide it there, that we can find it, how it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, the only thing what they ever wrote was it seems to be a town with lot of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] factories, because I see large pipes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the only thing what we ever got to know-- know.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
